I hope you will always feel love and support from all of your fans. I cannot wait to see where this next era will take us. But I know I will forever hold reputation close to my heart. For I know how much strength it has taken to create. #OneYearOfRep 

@taylornation13

You came out with reputation when I was trying to find my way through a difficult time in post college life. Between friends growing apart & a new office job, reputation was an outlet for me & helped me process my emotions. I will love & support forever & always. #OneYearOfRep
